<quantity box="[420,532,188,212]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.82" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" unit="mm" value="28.2">28.2 mm</quantity>
. For other measurements of referred specimens, see Appendix III (linear measurements) and Appendix I and II (body mass estimations).
</paragraph>
